{"tid":2435926,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"係夢中夢入面比鬼壓床","createTime":"2021-03-06T16:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T17:10:42.000Z","uid":318952,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd779e0c25d946ff1c5d566f7d8d336b7712d62","tid":2435926,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"想講返一件事<br />\n話說我今朝去練波，但係因為落雨取消咗啦，所以我就再瞓番。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓左唔知幾耐，我覺得自己醒咗但係我控制唔到自己個身體，於是我好努力咁由個口開始發力啦，「啊」左一陣我可以輕輕擘大眼，我見到一個女性半透明嘅野按住我膊頭，個口就好似張相咁對住我。呢個時候我仲未可以郁，佢愈黎愈面對面既時候，我更加努力咁繼續：「啊」同埋嘗試發力，因為呢樣野係我唯一可以做既事。最後我真係可以郁，拎返身體控制權，我身體既所以反射神經全部彈左一下，我原來係另一個夢入面比鬼壓床。<br />\n其實未完哂，我再訓返都係呢個情況，最後我出咗廳訓就完咗。<br />\n從來冇夢中夢呢個經歷，我唔知係我太攰定點啦，鬼壓床既經驗都係人生第二次，所以開Post請教各位ching<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkYH7AW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkYH7AW.jpg&h=e25a244d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大概係咁不過兩隻手係我膊頭"},{"pid":"4ebe10ccf384bf47e24b0f0cfad4db5871376d41","tid":2435926,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"雖然講故台但係真人真事"},{"pid":"be48a96a145c8a217482c7f0a67c0d8ed0c9a6e5","tid":2435926,"uid":318952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"如果個Po唔沉底有人應我再講埋另一個經歷"},{"pid":"e05409c74f34ad28a49e8c9a254a839fb9330fbc","tid":2435926,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"仲爆"},{"pid":"54c033fc8ffd7a52286858395813c2232f589f51","tid":2435926,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi